---
// FTC-compliant affiliate disclosure. Render at the top of any post containing affiliate links.
---

<aside class="affiliate-disclosure">
  <strong>Affiliate disclosure:</strong> This post contains affiliate links. If you sign up
  through these links we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. We only recommend
  tools we have tested ourselves. Recommendations are not influenced by commission rates —
  if we would not use the tool, we would not link to it.
</aside>

<style>
  .affiliate-disclosure {
    background: var(--sl-color-bg-nav);
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-hairline);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--sl-color-accent);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
  }
  .affiliate-disclosure strong { color: var(--sl-color-white); }
</style>
